  <chunk id="96ae683c7f824b0810ce750d60c15181b93181a4.c0" text="Establishment of Hairy Root Cultures by Agrobacterium Rhizogenes Mediated Transformation of Isatis Tinctoria L. for the Efficient Production of Flavonoids and Evaluation of Antioxidant Activities">
